name: Theodore Heath

He values honesty, humor, and intelligence and enjoys outdoor activities, video games, and reading in his spare time. This user is a Pisces and his MBTI personality type is INTJ. His desires for the future include having children, as he currently doesn't have any. He's also open to a long-term, monogamous relationship. His primary languages are English and Spanish.
